### ============================================
### 注册接口
### ============================================

### 邮箱注册
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/sign/up/email
Content-Type: application/json
{{apiVersionHeader}}

{
  "email": "normal@pardx.ai",
  "password": "3.1415926535",
  "name": "normal"
}

### 手机号注册
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/sign/up/mobile
Content-Type: application/json
{{apiVersionHeader}}

{
  "mobile": "18888880001",
  "password": "3.1415926",
  "name": "001",
  "code": "18888880009",
  "iddCode": "0086"
}

### ============================================
### Token 刷新
### ============================================

### 刷新 Token
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/sign/refresh/token?refresh=YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN
{{apiVersionHeader}}

### 通过 Cookie 刷新 Token
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/sign/in/cookie?refresh=YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN
{{apiVersionHeader}}

